==Transport links==
Herne Hill is served by [[London Buses|London bus]] routes [[London Buses route 3|3]], [[London Buses route 37|37]] (24 hours), [[London Buses route 68|68]], [[London Buses route 196|196]], [[London Buses route 201|201]], [[London Buses route 322|322]], [[London Buses route 468|468]], school route [[List of London school bus routes#690|690]] and night buses [[List of night buses in London#N3|N3]] and [[List of night buses in London#N68|N68]]. The nearest [[London Underground]] station is [[Brixton tube station|Brixton]].<ref>{{cite book |title= Buses from Herne Hill |year=2011 |publisher=[[Transport for London]] |url= http://www.tfl.gov.uk/tfl/gettingaround/maps/buses/pdf/hernehill-2125.pdf |accessdate=20 April 2012}}</ref>

